node.text:
Welcome to Praia do Camilo, a stunning secluded little beach only accessible by a staircase of around 200 steps. 

An absolute beauty of a sunrise spot. 

Lagos, Algarve 🇵🇹 🏖️ 

#visitalgarve #algarve #visitportugal
@darylbakerphotography fucking nailed it didn’t we, the one sunrise we got up for 😂
Some incredible golden hour here mate 👌🏻
@norths.north hahaha super sexy scene right there!
@theyorkshirewanderer you just canny beat them type of spots can you 😅🥹
Perfect just parked up at the top for this 🔥
You’re glowing 😍 that’s a beauty of a shot 🔥🔥
@benjy_johnson haha I know mate one and only time we got up early enough 😴
That time we actually got a sunrise 😂
@priceyphoto some way to kick start the day Pricy 🔥
@s_a_r_a_h_614 it’s doooopppeee isn’t it. Real nice little town too! You had the right idea 👏
Lagos is beautiful. I used to go for long weekends all the time😍
@sean_cgn siiiiick, it’s ace. Got a van or just a holiday?
@roamwithadam holiday with our van ;) Since we have our own van I reduced those van Jobs
@sean_cgn don’t blame you! Have a good time, it’s class.
So so good🔥 will be there in few weeks
@the__hiking__photographer Alexa play the stranglers - golden brown 🔥
@alexbowdensphotography I’ll take ya to the jewellery shop $$$$$
That light and colour is popping 🥵
@theyorkshirewanderer no point walking 20 miles for 20 likes x
@roamwithadam 1 like per mile ratio sounds about right, unless in the lakes when it’s 1000 like to 1 mile ratio 👀
@hikewithkate_ god you stink of jealousy! How’s your trip? Rory’s peak or whatever it’s called is a proper bucket list jobby!!
200 steps you say? Sounds like an Adam walk 👀
@andynethan I would love to watch the sunrise here with you

user.full_name: 🇵🇹 Visit, Explore and Discover Algarve, Portugal
